  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nRight now fuzz campaigns are defined by their number of runs. Itâ€™s also useful to instead define campaigns with a `timeout` which specifies the duration of the campaign, with a value of 0 meaning to run indefinitely. This is common in other fuzzers such as Echidna. \r\n\r\nIt would also be helpful to support config via cheat codes as discussed in #744, to allow some fuzz/invariant tests to be defined by number of runs with others defined by a timeout \r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
